TITLE: Implementing Basic Unit Test with QUnit
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates a basic synchronous test using QUnit.test() to verify a square function implementation. Shows how to use the assert argument for making test assertions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/qunitjs/qunit/blob/main/docs/api/QUnit/test.md#2025-04-12_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
function square (x) {
  return x * x;
}

QUnit.test('square()', function (assert) {
  assert.equal(square(2), 4);
  assert.equal(square(3), 9);
});
```

