TITLE: Basic QUnit HTML Test Setup
DESCRIPTION: Base HTML structure for running QUnit tests in a browser. Includes required QUnit CSS and JavaScript files along with placeholder elements for test results.
SOURCE: https://github.com/qunitjs/qunit/blob/main/docs/browser.md#2025-04-12_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: html
CODE:
```
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>QUnit</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://code.jquery.com/qunit/qunit-2.24.1.css">
<body>
  <div id="qunit"></div>
  <div id="qunit-fixture"></div>
  <script src="https://code.jquery.com/qunit/qunit-2.24.1.js"></script>
  <!-- <script src="your_app.test.js"></script> -->
</body>
</html>
```

