TITLE: Implementing Async Test with QUnit
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to use async/await syntax with QUnit.test() for asynchronous testing. Demonstrates testing of async operations using modern JavaScript features.
SOURCE: https://github.com/qunitjs/qunit/blob/main/docs/api/QUnit/test.md#2025-04-12_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
QUnit.test('Test with async-await', async function (assert) {
  const a = await fetchSquare(2);
  const b = await fetchSquare(3);

  assert.equal(a, 4);
  assert.equal(b, 9);
  assert.equal(await fetchSquare(5), 25);
});
```

