TITLE: Multiple step verifications in one test
DESCRIPTION: Example demonstrating how the internal buffer of steps is automatically reset after calling verifySteps(), allowing for multiple independent sequences of steps in a single test.
SOURCE: https://github.com/qunitjs/qunit/blob/main/docs/api/assert/verifySteps.md#2025-04-12_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
QUnit.test('multiple verifications example', function (assert) {
  assert.step('one');
  assert.step('two');
  assert.verifySteps(['one', 'two']);

  assert.step('three');
  assert.step('four');
  assert.verifySteps(['three', 'four']);
});
```

