TITLE: Writing a QUnit Test for the 'add' Function
DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to write a QUnit test for the 'add' function, including importing the function and defining a test suite.
SOURCE: https://github.com/qunitjs/qunit/blob/main/docs/cli.md#2025-04-12_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
