TITLE: Implementing Automatic Fixture Teardown in QUnit Tests
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how QUnit automatically cleans up DOM modifications between tests using an empty fixture. Shows two tests where the first test adds elements and the second test verifies they were automatically removed.
SOURCE: https://github.com/qunitjs/qunit/blob/main/docs/api/config/fixture.md#2025-04-12_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: html
CODE:
```
