LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
QUnit.test('example', async function (assert) {
  const p = feedMe();
  await assert.rejects(p, RangeError);

  try {
    await p;
  } catch (e) {
    assert.deepEqual(e.somedata, { foo: 'bar' });
  }
});
```

