TITLE: Creating or resetting release branch for QUnit release
DESCRIPTION: Command to create or reset the 'release' branch based on the latest main branch from origin.
SOURCE: https://github.com/qunitjs/qunit/blob/main/RELEASE.md#2025-04-12_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
git remote update && git checkout -B release -t origin/main
```

