TITLE: Creating and pushing git tag for QUnit release
DESCRIPTION: Commands to create a signed git tag for the release and push it to the remote repository.
SOURCE: https://github.com/qunitjs/qunit/blob/main/RELEASE.md#2025-04-12_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
git tag -s "@VERSION" -m "Release @VERSION"
git push --tags
```

